{"tid":967893,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"道指全日瀉660點　蘋果大跌近10%","createTime":"2019-01-03T22:11:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T01:54:23.000Z","uid":26418,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0abadfd866c1686f4e59fb5a4b3aa6848a9c77c5","tid":967893,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T22:11:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1436365_1_20190104053659.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1436365_1_20190104053659.jpg&h=3d1c60f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>美股三大指數顯著低收逾2至3%，道指挫660點。（美聯社）</em><br />\n<br />\n美股大幅下挫，美國製造業數據遠差過預期，加上蘋果罕有發出盈利預警，都加劇市場對環球經濟放緩的憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n道瓊斯指數一度急瀉逾700點，低見22638點，其後略為收窄跌幅，收市仍跌660點，報22686點，跌幅2.8%。<br />\n<br />\n標普500指數收市報2447點，下跌62點，跌幅約2.5%。<br />\n<br />\n納斯達克指數顯著低收3%，報6463點，下挫202點。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果股價大跌約10%，創逾一年半以來收市最低，市值單日蒸發逾746億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1436365-20190104.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1436365-20190104.htm&d=ZfTIuG8AAOXkUNfKl4Vmkmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=ff61a57a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1436365-20190104.htm&h=190a2bc2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1436365-20190104.htm</a>"},{"pid":"14998f46abfa439bd42cedf71df0bc42422d89f7","tid":967893,"uid":75072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T22:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e2f3465955caf08afd77cc3d1be6e1ab00083bf","tid":967893,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T23:08:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nD重貨傻撚happy new year<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45179dd77d0e94d0df1fa